
These allows us to send dynamic data in our html with the help of express, There are few templating engines available
such as express handlebars, or pug or ejs (embedde js templating)


EJS VIEW ENGINE

 Installing ejs locally : npm install ejs

 ejs will look for the views folder by default

 in ejs, we define our view file with a .ejs extension

 ejs files contain html with ejs speicific code